    <mxCell id="43" value="GET /v1/environments/{envId}/users/{userId}&lt;br&gt;Authorization: Bearer &amp;lt;Token 3&amp;gt;" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;html=1;fontSize=10;labelBackgroundColor=#ffffff;" edge="1" source="41" target="42" parent="1">
      <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"/>
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="44" value="&lt;i&gt;MCP Server holds both tokens simultaneously:&lt;br&gt;Token 2 = delegation proof (user sub + act chain) &amp;nbsp;|&amp;nbsp; Token 3 = PingOne Management API credential&lt;/i&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f8f8f8;strokeColor=#cccccc;align=center;fontSize=11;" vertex="1" parent="1">
      <mxGeometry x="640" y="560" width="640" height="58" as="geometry"/>
    </mxCell>

    <!-- ── SpEL expression (act claim) ── -->
    <mxCell id="50" value="&lt;b&gt;SpEL expression — BX Finance MCP Server resource → Attribute Mappings → act claim:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Courier New&quot; style=&quot;font-size:10px&quot;&gt;(#root.context.requestData.subjectToken?.may_act?.sub != null &amp;amp;&amp;amp; #root.context.requestData.subjectToken?.may_act?.sub == #root.context.requestData.actorToken?.aud?.get(0))&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;? #root.context.requestData.subjectToken?.may_act : null&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fffde7;strokeColor=#f0cd00;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=11;" vertex="1" parent="1">
      <mxGeometry x="20" y="662" width="1260" height="72" as="geometry"/>
    </mxCell>

